            <sentence>
                <offset>0</offset>
                <text>﻿Patient 4 (V-9; Fig. 1A) was born in Anjouan Island (Comoros Islands).</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>72</offset>
                <text>This male patient had been referred to Mayotte Island at the age of 7 years.</text>
